data.description: IMPROVED PRICE!! READY TO MOVE IN! GREAT LOCATION! Your opportunity awaits you with this beautifully renovated house located in a quiet community, it has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, and it has a 2-car garage. NO HOA or CDD. The seller planned to make this home his dream home and did not skip on making essential improvements to make this home last for many years. When you walk in, you are instantly greeted with that "at home" feeling natural lighting throughout. The kitchen opens to the large dining room, perfect for family Sunday dinners. You can't miss the newly remodeled master bathroom and updated second bathroom. The kitchen is brand new with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, the air conditioning is new, just installed on October 23rd, new sliding door and garage door with new motor. The roof is metal and was installed only a few years ago. The yard is fenced with a vinyl fence and a covered porch for the entire family to enjoy. Freshly painted outside and inside. new carpets in room 2 and 3.  Located across from Limona Park and only 5-10 minutes to an array of shopping and dining options, plus just 20-25 minutes tops to downtown Tampa and 30 minutes to the Tampa International Airport! Great access to all interstate access with I-75, I-4, and the Selmon Expressway all within 10 minutes away, this location can't be beat!  Don't let this beautiful house go, coordinate your appointment today and bring your best offer.
